any trade will ever be found in you again, and no sound of a millstone will ever be heard in you

00:10:59.059 --> 00:11:08.100
again. No light of a lamp will ever shine in you again, and no voice of a bridegroom and of a bride

00:11:08.100 --> 00:11:13.779
will ever be heard in you again. For your merchants were the top-ranking men of the earth,

00:11:14.419 --> 00:11:21.460
and by your spiritual practices all the nations were misled. Yes, in her was found the blood of

00:11:21.460 --> 00:11:28.419
prophets, and of holy ones, and of all those who have been slaughtered on the earth. After this,

00:11:29.139 --> 00:11:36.100
I heard what seemed to be a loud voice of a great crowd in heaven. They said,

00:11:36.100 --> 00:11:52.740
pray to salvation and the glory and the power, because his judgments are true and righteous,

00:11:52.740 --> 00:12:02.019
for he has executed judgment on the great prostitute who corrupted the earth with her sexual immorality,

00:12:02.019 --> 00:12:10.659
and he has avenged the blood of his slaves and is on her hands. And right away, for the second time,

00:12:10.820 --> 00:12:18.190
they said,

00:12:24.990 --> 00:12:34.269
Yes, praise jaw. Why? False religious leaders were responsible for the death of the prophets,

00:12:34.269 --> 00:12:39.870
and of Jesus Christ himself. Later, the disciple Stephen asked the religious leaders,

00:12:40.269 --> 00:12:44.830
which one of the prophets did your forefathers not persecute?

00:12:46.190 --> 00:12:50.669
Yes, they killed those who announced in advance the coming of the righteous one,

00:12:51.389 --> 00:12:57.789
whose betrayers and murderers you have now become. Instead of taking Stephen's rebuke to heart,

00:12:58.830 --> 00:13:05.840
they murdered him too, that same day. In the century since Stephen's day,

00:13:06.799 --> 00:13:13.759
false religion has continued to mislead, to slaughter, and to corrupt the earth with her sexual immorality.

00:13:14.639 --> 00:13:21.360
So once again, we can ask, why praise jaw? The heavenly chorus answers,

00:13:22.000 --> 00:13:30.240
because God's judgments are true and righteous. Our just God, Jehovah, will make sure that false

00:13:30.240 --> 00:13:35.759
religion will never again defile this world and harm his loyal servants.

00:13:37.519 --> 00:13:44.559
The destruction of Babel on the Great marks the beginning of what Jesus called the Great Tribulation.

00:13:46.399 --> 00:13:53.120
After false religion is gone, what comes next? The book of Ezekiel foretells that the nations will

00:13:53.120 --> 00:13:59.919
attack Jehovah's people, coming like a vast army and like clouds covering the land.

00:14:00.960 --> 00:14:05.919
But this is not the first time that the political system has acted against Jehovah and his people.

00:14:07.519 --> 00:14:13.120
Many nations have fiercely opposed true worship. They've banned our meetings and our

00:14:13.120 --> 00:14:19.840
preaching work. In prison, men and women, old and young, for the so-called crime of owning a Bible,

00:14:20.559 --> 00:14:27.279
or talking about their God, some of our brothers and sisters have even been tortured for their faith.

00:14:28.960 --> 00:14:35.840
Of course, as long as Jehovah allows human governments to rule over us, we respect them.

00:14:37.039 --> 00:14:39.600
And not all governments have actively opposed us.

00:14:41.120 --> 00:14:46.159
Still, human government itself is insulting to Jehovah.

00:14:46.799 --> 00:14:52.159
Human rulers suggest that they could rule better than the King of kings and Lord of

00:14:52.159 --> 00:15:01.840
Lords, Christ Jesus, how arrogant. No wonder then that once these political powers attack God's people,

00:15:02.799 --> 00:15:12.320
Jesus will take action. In Revelation 19, note the actions that Jesus takes against the Anglo-American

00:15:12.320 --> 00:15:18.399
world power portrayed as a false prophet, and the entire political system described as the

00:15:18.399 --> 00:15:25.200
kings of the earth and the wild beast. We'll begin reading at Revelation 19, verse 11.

00:15:45.230 --> 00:15:53.389
And on his head are many diadems. He has a name written that no one knows but he himself,

00:15:53.389 --> 00:16:01.070
and he is clothed with an outer garment, stained with blood, and he is called by the name

00:16:01.070 --> 00:16:08.350
the Word of God. Also, the armies in heaven were following him on white horses,

00:16:09.309 --> 00:16:16.350
and they were clothed in white, clean, fine linen. Ask, out of his mouth,

00:16:16.350 --> 00:16:23.470
protrudes a sharp, long sword with which to strike the nations, and he will shepherd them with

00:16:23.470 --> 00:16:31.710
a rod of iron. Moreover, he treads the winepress of the fury of the wrath of God the Almighty.

00:16:32.429 --> 00:16:41.870
On his outer garment, yes, on his thigh, he has a name written, King of kings, and Lord of Lords.

