birds that fly in mid-Heaven, come here. Be gathered together to the great evening meal of God

00:16:59.149 --> 00:17:05.150
so that you may eat the flesh of kings, and the flesh of military commanders, and the flesh

00:17:05.150 --> 00:17:11.390
of straw men, and the flesh of horses, and of those seated on them, and the flesh of all,

00:17:12.029 --> 00:17:16.910
of free men, as well as of slaves, and of small ones, and great.

00:17:17.710 --> 00:17:24.829
And I saw the wild beast, and the kings of the earth, and their armies, gathered together

00:17:24.829 --> 00:17:32.910
to wage war against the one seated on the horse, and against his army, and the wild beast was caught,

00:17:33.470 --> 00:17:40.269
and along with it the false prophet that performed in front of it the signs with which he misled

00:17:40.269 --> 00:17:47.390
those who received the mark of the wild beast, and those who worship its image, while still alive,

00:17:48.109 --> 00:17:55.950
they both were hurled into the fiery lake that burns with sulfur, but the rest were killed off with

00:17:55.950 --> 00:18:04.430
the long sword that proceeded out of the mouth of the one seated on the horse, and all the birds were

00:18:04.430 --> 00:18:13.920
food with their flesh. Who else but Christ Jesus would lead the heavenly forces to the battle of

00:18:13.920 --> 00:18:21.599
Armageddon? False religion has already been destroyed. Now Jesus turns his attention to what

00:18:21.599 --> 00:18:28.240
remains of Satan's wicked world. It's political and commercial systems. He dismantles,

00:18:28.880 --> 00:18:35.839
destroys, and brings to nothing all who oppose true worship on earth, but enemies of true

00:18:35.839 --> 00:18:44.799
worship still remain. Who are they? And what does Jesus do about them? Follow along at Revelation 20

00:18:44.799 --> 00:18:54.910
versus one through three. And I saw an angel coming down out of heaven with the key of the abyss,

