Those who've been loyal to Jehovah will then witness astonishing things. Let's consider one of them

00:20:14.339 --> 00:20:24.819
beginning at Revelation 20 verse 12. And I saw the dead, the great and the small, standing before

00:20:24.819 --> 00:20:33.220
the throne and scrolls were opened, but another scroll was opened. It is the scroll of life.

00:20:34.259 --> 00:20:40.259
