but billions of others who will be resurrected from the dead. And at the end of the millennial reign,

00:21:31.279 --> 00:21:38.640
death itself will finally be gone. It's hurled into the lake of fire as irretrievable as a piece

00:21:38.640 --> 00:21:46.299
of paper thrown into a raging furnace. What will life be like under Kingdom rule?

00:21:47.980 --> 00:21:58.589
How we love the promises at Revelation 21 verse 4, and God will wipe out every tear from their eyes.

00:21:59.549 --> 00:22:15.089
